As a global business, Katun operates in a multi-currency environment and generated ~63% of revenue in currencies other than the US dollar from 2014-2016; as a result, changes in foreign currency exchange rates can have a significant impact on the Company’s operating results
Revenue growth in US dollars was adversely impacted by the weakening underlying currencies vs. the US dollar as highlighted in the chart below
